OL,3,CMan charged with gross negligence
OL,4,Cmanslaughter following death of Jay
OL,5,CCartmell
OL,7,FA man has been charged with gross
OL,8,Fnegligence manslaughter following the
OL,9,Fdeath of eight-year-old Jay Cartmell
OL,10,Fin September 2024.
OL,12,FJay died at Warcop in Cumbria whilst
OL,13,Fhe was out shooting rabbits.
OL,15,FAllan Thursby, 64, of Dent Place,
OL,16,FCleator Moor, was arrested to 28
OL,17,FSeptember 2024 and had been on police
OL,18,Fbail since. He has now been charged
OL,19,Fwith gross negligence manslaughter.
